## 9. Role Visibility

|Action|Org Admin|Internal Finance|Store Manager|Sales Team|
|---|---|---|---|---|
|View Customer List/Detail|✅|✅|✅|✅|
|Create/Edit Customer|✅|✅|✅|✅|
|View Lifetime Spend / Purchase History|✅|✅|✅|✅|
|Deactivate Customer|✅|✅|❌|❌|

> Sales Team and Store Manager are given create/edit access here since customer capture typically happens at the point of sale, on the shop floor — unlike Purchase-side data, this isn't cost-sensitive information, so the usual purchase-price restriction doesn't apply to this module.

